        <head>Postcard</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Send you a postcard </l>
          <l>From a place you'll never like </l>
          <l>The day it will snow hard </l>
          <l>I'm pissed around a wrinkled line </l>
          <l>Can't find my own stuff </l>
          <l>You're like the passport in my drawer </l>
          <l>Being so peaceful </l>
          <l>You're like a cloud inside my car</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
